text: Kavindu Kulasekara (born 20 August 1995) is a Sri Lankan first-class cricketer. He was part of Sri Lanka's squad for the 2014 ICC Under-19 Cricket World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Kandy District cricketers Category:Cricketers from Colombo
